            MYSQL USER CREATION

1.  How to login mysql
    mysql -u root -p
       or 
    mysql -p

2.  How to check mysql users
    select user from mysql.users;

3.  How to check mysql hosts
    select host from mysql.users;

4.  How to create a new user 
    syntax
    create user 'username'@'localhost' identified by 'password';

5.  How to assing a password
    set password for usarname@host=password('12345');

6.  How to give  privelages on user
    syntax
    grant [type of permision] on [data base name].[tablename] to'username'@'localhost'; 
       
7.  How to edit the permission granted
    syntax
    revoke [type of permision] on [data base name].[table name] to'username'@'localhost'; 
    
8.  How to delete a user
    drop user 'username'@'localhost';

9.  How to check the database
    show databases;

10. How to create a new databases
    create database databasename;

11. How to delete a database
    drop database databasename;

12. how to see user database table
    use databasename;

13. How to check the table
    show tables;

14. How to create a table
    create table newdatabasename(columnname varchar(40));

15. How to open the table
    describe tablename;

16. How to Add Information to a mysql Table
    INSERT INTO `tablename` (`id`,`name`,`food`,`confirmed`,`signup_date`) VALUES (NULL, "John", "Casserole","Y", '2012-04-11');

17. How to open the add information or table information in mysql table
    select *(you want see id or name some this thing's) from tablename;

18. How to Update Information in the Table
    update tablename set (you change option) (`confrimed`= 'y') where `tablename`.`name`='columname';

19. How to Add a column 
    ALTER TABLE tablename ADD columname (VARCHAR(40)) after name;

20. How to Delete a column 
    ALTER TABLE tablename DROP columname;

21. How to Delete a row 
    DELETE from [table name] where [column name]=[field text];

22. How to backup and import on mysql
    $sudo mysqldump -u username -p databasename to backup > backup-filename.sql
    To see the backup file
     $ls .sql files are backup 
    After than delete one database 

23. How to restore and backup on mysql database
    mysql -u username -p newdatabasename < filename.sql


